{"tid":788872,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"奇洛李維斯假戲真做同stranger things女星結婚多年","createTime":"2018-08-21T23:02:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T00:07:28.000Z","uid":165773,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"d38373c3606bb6e1e64c60e89e6b4d72472af674","tid":788872,"uid":165773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-21T23:02:08.000Z","msg":"Winona Ryder<br />\nKeanu Reeves<br />\n最近Winona在訪問透露驚人秘密<br />\n她與K先生於1992年拍吸血鬼一戲<br />\n當中結婚一幕 <br />\n請了真正做牧師既牧師演牧師 <br />\n使該場儀式具法律效力<br />\n拍完該場戲之後<br />\n兩人正式成為了夫妻<br />\n<br />\n今年兩人將在銀幕再度合作<br />\nDestination Wedding <br />\n於美國八月三十一日首映田<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/keanu-reeves-winona-ryder-married-dracula-wedding-francis-ford-coppola-a8501021.html#\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Farts-entertainment%2Ffilms%2Fnews%2Fkeanu-reeves-winona-ryder-married-dracula-wedding-francis-ford-coppola-a8501021.html%23&d=bkn8ywxYB2KZgfajZiddNE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=dc5f217e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/films/news/keanu-reeves-winona-ryder-married-dracula-wedding-francis-ford-coppola-a8501021.html#</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/22/065841_339d4b2308b6c8c81b9979c205041245.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F065841_339d4b2308b6c8c81b9979c205041245.png&h=164e79ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/22/065854_ffa776aa770329dea26a0c38038e9e29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F22%2F065854_ffa776aa770329dea26a0c38038e9e29.png&h=aca46be6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/22/065913_e05d1d26428c18c483004fae4f21e734.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2